headline: Generac (GNRC) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of power generation products company Generac (NYSE:GNRC) rose the morning session after it continued to receive positive sentiment from Wall Street analysts who held a consensus "Strong Buy" rating on the stock.
